SUMMARY—Makes appropriations and authorizations for certain
compensation and benefits for state employees
represented by a bargaining unit. (BDR S-1247)
FISCAL NOTE: Effect on Local Government: No.
Effect on the State: Contains Appropriation not included
in Executive Budget.
